Package: twinkle
Version: 0.0.3
Title: Load Balanced Shiny Server
Description: Creates a load balanced, authenticated, shiny server,
  running over https using docker and haproxy.  This package provides
  the utility code designed to do housekeeping configuration for the
  system and is not designed to be used in a standalone capacity.
